					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like the idea a lot, but it seems so utterly unstoppable and that it's a bit hard to take it seriously. And yes, to begin with, it's obviously whimsical in nature, though I think there should be <em>some</em> repercussions if it's performed wrong or something so that it's less of an unstoppable cheat code only some can handle and more of a delicate art form. However, it's still pretty creative on its own.</p> 
