				<wikidot:authorName>Scorpion451</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1918720</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p><em>Warning: Containment Breach In Progress</em> the PA system intoned for the twentieth time.</p> <p>Solemly, Phil stopped and turned back toward the roars echoing down the hallway.</p> <p>He removed his tie, folding it neatly before trading it for a headband from his gym bag.</p> <p>&quot;Go. I'll buy you time&quot; he muttered as he slid the elastic over his receding hairline.</p> <p>&quot;If I don't make it&#8230;&quot; he called over the protests of his fleeing coworkers.</p> <p>His eyes closed, and he unconsciously reached up to comb a long-abdicated crown of afro. &quot;&#8230;tell Linda that last year's Christmas party was the best night of my life.&quot;</p> <p>Flickering emergency lights blended with memories of strobe-lit dancefloors as he pointed to the sky.</p> <p>Phil began to dance.</p> </blockquote> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
